</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Tavares, M. S. &amp; Santana, W." box="[557,843,1942,1968]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="201 - 227" refId="ref30834" refString="Tavares, M. S. &amp; Santana, W. (2018) Refining the genus Rochinia A. Milne-Edwards, 1875: reinstatement of Scyramathia A. Milne-Edwards, 1880 and Anamathia Smith, 1885, and a new genus for Amathia crassa A. Milne-Edwards, 1879, with notes on its ontogeny (Crustacea: Brachyura: Epialtidae). Zootaxa, 4418 (3), 201 - 227. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4418.3.1" type="journal article" year="2018">Tavares &amp; Santana, 2018</bibRefCitation>
